ssed, 0 failed), cargo clippy -- -D warnings (clean), cargo fmt --check (clean on all modified files).\",\n      \"order\": 10,\n      \"status\": \"completed\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"validation_evidence\": [\n    \"cargo test: 683 passed, 0 failed, 0 ignored\",\n    \"cargo clippy -- -D warnings: no warnings or errors\",\n    \"cargo fmt --check: all modified files clean; only pre-existing formatting diffs in unrelated tests/unit/agent_execution_test.rs\",\n    \"Amendment 1: tracing::warn! at fs.rs:2832-2837 logs 'contract violation — requested_run_id is Some but requested_started_at is None; this bypasses the started_at guard on runless terminal candidates' before returning None\",\n    \"Amendment 2: merge_attempt_entries_fills_all_optional_fields test covers both fill-from-secondary (run_id, plan_hash, snapshot_plan_hash_at_creation, outcome_detail, finished_at) and no-overwrite-existing paths, catches forgotten merge lines when new optional fields are added\",\n    \"Amendment 3: effective_plan_hash = plan_hash.map(str::to_owned) — no snapshot fallback. snapshot_plan_hash_at_creation still recorded for provenance. plan_hash_auto_populated_from_snapshot test confirms plan_hash is None after start, then filled during completion via safe_plan_hash_backfill\",\n    \"Amendment 4: safe_plan_hash_backfill None-provenance branch returns false unconditionally. running_entry_created_before_plan_is_not_backfilled_on_revisit test confirms legacy entry with snapshot_plan_hash_at_creation=None stays plan_hash=None through replay and completion\",\n    \"safe_backfill_fills_plan_hash_when_snapshot_unchanged: bead-provenance with explicit provenance still gets backfilled during finalization via the Some-provenance branch — provenance-based backfill unaffected\",\n    \"safe_backfill_skips_when_snapshot_evolved: entry with v1 provenance stays plan_hash=None when snapshot has advanced to v2 — plan-evolution safety check unaffected\",\n    \"terminal_replay_after_plan_evolution_succ